# --  Table of variables.  -------------------------------------------------------------------------

--  B-01: Core product (land system model forcing data).  ------------------------------------------

Variable	Long name				Category	Unit	Resolution	

Temp		2 m air temperature			B-01		K	03hr, 0.10deg
Pres		Surface air pressure			B-01		Pa	03hr, 0.10deg
SHum		Specific humidity			B-01		kg kg	03hr, 0.10deg
Wind		10 m wind speed				B-01		m s-1	03hr, 0.10deg
SRad		Downward shortwave radiation at surface	B-01		W m-2	03hr, 0.10deg
LRad		Downward longwave radiation at surface	B-01		W m-2	03hr, 0.10deg
Prec		Precipitation rate			B-01		mm hr-1	03hr, 0.10deg

--  B-02: Extended product (derived from land system model forcing data).  -------------------------

Variable	Long name				Category	Unit	Resolution	

BCPr		Bias-corrected precipitation rate	B-02		mm hr-1	03hr, 0.10deg
